{"tid":2142192,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血公民黃兆健：假若大家衷心「支持香港醫護」，明白「血庫」對醫療服務、公民社會的重要，請身體力行支持，並呼籲朋友捐血。","createTime":"2020-08-06T08:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T17:39:21.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"cbbb1df5ee82e8c29afe281ec9488a2602ba02a6","tid":2142192,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"黃兆健：<br />\n【捐血救人，捐一次血救三個人！】<br />\n「捐血救人」作為文明社會的德行，在當今香港卻來得「難能可貴」。暴政讓人民被恐懼、憤怒蒙蔽，眾多愚昧的說法呼籲別人罷捐。<br />\n假若大家衷心「支持香港醫護」，並明白「血庫」對醫療服務、甚至整個公民社會的重要，請大家身體力行支持，並呼籲身邊朋友捐血。<br />\n日前我在大埔文娛中心外流動捐血車完成捐血，開放時間如下，請大家多加支持。<br />\n開放日期：2020年08月03日 - 21日 <br />\n地址：大埔安邦路大埔文娛中心外 <br />\n開放時間：11時30分 - 19時00分 <br />\n電話：2710 1234 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEBLVPo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEBLVPo.jpg&h=4e9af5d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"904a21f7109fb505d0498806e64b263c2a02e4a5","tid":2142192,"uid":254183,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:49:59.000Z","msg":"捐你老母捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41399fa1ac48a17475509708bd5a2a59c06a3f31","tid":2142192,"uid":70487,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:51:10.000Z","msg":"佢唔認黃，<br />\n<br />\n請叫佢熱狗兆健"},{"pid":"272d0d1c850f65e2e9f7bba12b40d9772fa538a6","tid":2142192,"uid":48060,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:52:07.000Z","msg":"佢地存在真係為咗分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf366dacbda92c5059b9db5757cf379751103f56","tid":2142192,"uid":153600,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"其實熱狗真係同保皇嗰班有冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5dad91a15f986e3c582356b3a191875ee9464b","tid":2142192,"uid":34223,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime"